OL,3,CSingapore Airlines flight hit by
OL,4,Cturbulence plummeted 54 metres in four
OL,5,Cseconds
OL,7,FA Singapore Airlines flight which
OL,8,Fencountered severe turbulence during
OL,9,Fwhich a 73-year-old British man died,
OL,10,Fdropped 54 metres in just four
OL,11,Fseconds, an investigation has found.
OL,13,FThe Transport Safety Investigation
OL,14,FBureau of Singapore (TSIB) found the
OL,15,Fplane experienced a rapid change in
OL,16,Fgravitational force, causing
OL,17,Fpassengers who were not wearing
OL,18,Fseatbelts to be thrown upwards.
