OL,4,Cturbulence plummeted 54 metres in four
OL,5,Cseconds
OL,7,FFlight SQ321 was en route to Singapore
OL,8,Ffrom London Heathrow when it began to
OL,9,Fexperience slight turbulence as it
OL,10,Fflew over an area where thunderstorms
OL,11,Fwere developing above Myanmar at
OL,12,F8:49am UK time on 21 May, the report
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FAs this slight turbulence set in about
OL,16,Ften hours after departure, the plane
OL,17,Fexperienced a rise in altitude by
OL,18,Faround 110 metres. At this point, the
OL,19,Fpilot announced the fasten seatbelt
OL,20,Fsign had been turned on.
