OL,5,Cseconds
OL,7,FJust eight seconds later, a rapid
OL,8,Fchange in gravitational force caused
OL,9,Fan altitude drop of around 54 metres.
OL,11,FThe pilots disengaged autopilot,
OL,12,Fstabilised the aircraft and then re-
OL,13,Fengaged the autopilot.
OL,15,FThey then declared a medical emergency
OL,16,Fand diverted to Bangkok's Suvarnabhumi
OL,17,FAirport at 3.45pm local time (9.45am
OL,18,FUK time), where a total of 104
OL,19,Fpatients were taken to hospital and
OL,20,Fmedical clinics.
