OL,7,FTheatre director Geoffrey Ralph
OL,8,FKitchen from south Gloucestershire
OL,9,Fdied during the incident after
OL,10,Fsuffering a suspected heart attack.
OL,12,FA total of 104 patients were taken to
OL,13,Fhospital and medical clinics in
OL,14,FBangkok, where the plane was diverted.
OL,15,FSix British people were taken to ICU.
