OL,7,FIn a statement at the time, Singapore
OL,8,FAirlines said: "We can confirm that
OL,9,Fthere are injuries and one fatality on
OL,10,Fboard the Boeing 777-300ER. There were
OL,11,Fa total of 211 passengers and 18 crew
OL,12,Fon board.
OL,14,F"Singapore Airlines offers its deepest
OL,15,Fcondolences to the family of the
OL,16,Fdeceased."
OL,18,FThe TSIB said investigations are
OL,19,Fongoing into the incident.
